%                          nirantaradhyānakaraṇāt     nijasvarūpaṃ prakāśanasāmarthyaṃ bhavati / \E
%                          \om until .....            nijasvarūpaprakāśasāmarthyaṃ     bhavati / \P
%                          niraṃtaraṃ dhyānakaraṇāt   nijasvarūpaprakāśasāmarthyaṃ     bhavati / \B
